==English==
===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ˈɛn.i.bɑd.i/ or /-bʊd.i/

===Pronoun===
# Any one out of an indefinite number of persons; anyone; any person.
# {{colloquial}} A person of consideration or standing.  Usually used in the negative, as in ''he's not anybody'' means he is not important socially.
